      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="set_user_time_zone" data-step-uuid="DC77F7F0-109C-0138-CAD5-12F2183ABDFB">
    <h2 id="set_user_time_zone" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Select Pronouns</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/026/801/original/39d0538b-64b7-49df-a3c0-6a9bd690121c.png" srcset="" alt="Select Pronouns" height="547" width="523">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_DC781D30-109C-0138-CAD7-12F2183ABDFB" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the <strong>Pronouns</strong> drop-down menu, select your personal pronouns.</p>
<p><strong>Notes:</strong> </p>
<ul>
<li>If the Pronouns drop-down menu does not display in your User Settings, your institution has not enabled this feature.</li>
<li>Pronoun options are managed by your institution. You cannot add pronoun options.</li>
</ul>
  </div>
</div>
 
